            </m:mrow>
            <m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{g rSub { size 8{1} }  \( τ \) = {  { langle E \( t \) E rSup { size 8{*} }  \( t+τ \)  rangle }  over  { langle E \( t \) E rSup { size 8{*} }  \( t \)  rangle } } } {}</m:annotation>
